_sText: This is a map with inspiration from a laser-game arena. Before you start flaming me for bad lightning, I just have to say: This is how it should be! The original place also have lightning that makes it hard to see, and you bump into walls all the time. :::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: Objective: Kill your opponents, or get across the map and buzzkill them. :::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: :::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: Weapons: You start with an M4A1, Deagle, full Armor, and a HE Grenade. :::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: The thing about the button, is that in the real laser game, you have to shoot a sensor or something to win. Here, you press a button. Added a skybox around the map so you can NoClip/Spectate around the map to get a better overwiew. If you find this map confusing, just run around a little, you'll get the hang of it soon ;) Before you flame me for stealing a map name, I didn't, the laser arena in the real world is called Wasteland.
